Output demo.gif
Set Shell bash
Set FontSize 22
Set Width 1000
Set Height 540
Set Padding 30
Set BorderRadius 10
Set TypingSpeed 55ms

Hide
Type "cd ~/Documents/GitHub/simdjson_dart && clear && export PS1='$ '" Enter
Sleep 900ms
Show
Sleep 500ms
Type "dart run bench/demo.dart"
Sleep 800ms
Enter
Sleep 8s
Sleep 1500ms
